352
00:12:10,463 --> 00:12:12,973
Ted, okay, I insist
that you tell me why not.

353
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,030
No way.

354
00:12:14,067 --> 00:12:16,967
Answer the question.
It's... it's for the bride.

355
00:12:17,004 --> 00:12:18,114
I'm not gonna answer
the question,

356
00:12:18,138 --> 00:12:21,238
because you know the answer.

357
00:12:22,409 --> 00:12:24,079
