any of this is 'cause

361
00:12:31,584 --> 00:12:34,394
I know that it's not gonna
change anything.

362
00:12:34,421 --> 00:12:36,461
You and Barney are getting
married today.

363
00:12:36,489 --> 00:12:39,259
If I have to hold the shotgun
myself, it's happening.

364
00:12:39,292 --> 00:12:42,102
