376
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:10,120
Because I'm not gonna be there.

377
00:13:10,157 --> 00:13:11,957
I'm moving to Chicago.

378
00:13:18,165 --> 00:13:20,265
You're moving
to Chicago?
That's right.

379
00:13:20,300 --> 00:13:21,770
