Mm-hmm.

399
00:14:23,463 --> 00:14:26,403
Number four,
boats, boats, boats.

400
00:14:26,433 --> 00:14:28,173
Number three, Karen.
Mm.

401
00:14:28,201 --> 00:14:32,271
Number two, uh, Zoey.
She made both lists.

402
00:14:32,305 --> 00:14:35,835
