406
00:14:40,981 --> 00:14:44,121
So I was at your apartment
stealing your mail,

407
00:14:44,151 --> 00:14:47,391
and apparently there's
some chick named Victoria

408
00:14:47,420 --> 00:14:49,060
sending you jewelry

409
