of the wedding gift master!

415
00:15:02,135 --> 00:15:03,765
Now bring it back
to me right now!

416
00:15:03,803 --> 00:15:05,813
Fine. Meet me
at the Bow Bridge

417
00:15:05,838 --> 00:15:07,568
in Central Park in one hour.

418
00:15:07,607 --> 00:15:10,037
And by the way,
I want Kenny back.

419
00:15:10,077 --> 00:15:11,037
Who's Kenny?!

420
00:15:11,078 --> 00:15:12,478
My pet tarantula.

421
00:15:12,512 --> 00:15:13,952
(gasps)

422
00:15:13,981 --> 00:15:16,081
By the way, I love your hair.

423
00:15:16,116 --> 00:15:17,546
I love your hair!

424
00:15:17,584 --> 00:15:18,824
Imaginary women, right?

425
00:15:18,851 --> 00:15:22,961
I need everyone
to just be quiet, please.

426
00:15:22,990 --> 00:15:28,060
Look, I know that I could
have handled all of this better.

427
00:15:28,095 --> 00:15:31,125
But setting aside the fact
that all of our friends are here

428
00:15:31,164 --> 00:15:32,634
and that we don't speak Italian,

429
00:15:32,665 --> 00:15:35,235
if we stay in New York, we both
get to follow our dreams.

430
00:15:35,268 --> 00:15:36,598
Are we really gonna go someplace

431
00:15:36,636 --> 00:15:38,466
