It makes sense to stay here.

436
00:15:46,146 --> 00:15:47,176
Even I know that.

437
00:15:47,214 --> 00:15:48,924
You do?

438
00:15:48,948 --> 00:15:51,348
So... I win?

439
00:15:52,319 --> 00:15:55,189
Well, then, ho, hey, ho.

440
00:15:55,222 --> 00:15:59,292
