446
00:16:10,570 --> 00:16:12,710
if you keep cutting me out
of decisions,

447
00:16:12,739 --> 00:16:16,309
if you keep using words
like "winning" and "losing"

448
00:16:16,343 --> 00:16:17,983
when you talk
about our marriage.

449
00:16:18,011 --> 00:16:21,151
It's not like it'll happen
all at once,

450
00:16:21,181 --> 00:16:23,821
but if you keep acting
this way,

451
00:16:23,850 --> 00:16:27,020
little by little,

452
00:16:27,054 --> 00:16:28,164
