for her. That's crazy!

476
00:17:21,108 --> 00:17:23,008
That's more than crazy.

477
00:17:23,042 --> 00:17:24,842
I don't think there's a word
for what that is!

478
00:17:24,877 --> 00:17:27,147
Actually, there is a word
for that. It's "love."

479
00:17:28,315 --> 00:17:30,275
I'm in love with her, okay?

480
00:17:30,317 --> 00:17:32,887
If you're looking for the word
that means caring about someone

481
00:17:32,919 --> 00:17:35,259
beyond all rationality
and wanting them to have

482
00:17:35,288 --> 00:17:36,958
