no matter how much

483
00:17:36,989 --> 00:17:38,159
it destroys you, it's love!

484
00:17:39,459 --> 00:17:41,729
And when you love someone,
you just, you...

485
00:17:41,761 --> 00:17:43,231
you don't stop, ever.

486
00:17:43,263 --> 00:17:45,973
Even when people roll their
eyes or call you crazy.

487
00:17:45,998 --> 00:17:47,968
Even then. Especially then!

488
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:50,740
You just-- you don't give up!
Because if I could give up...

489
00:17:50,770 --> 00:17:53,810
if I could just, you know,
take the whole world's advice

490
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:56,980
