to see it.

516
00:19:31,170 --> 00:19:34,410
Good luck, boys.

517
00:19:34,441 --> 00:19:37,211
Take care of
the game for me.

518
00:19:37,244 --> 00:19:39,554
We will.

519
00:19:41,113 --> 00:19:43,983
